      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Option A is the best fit for a \"prestigious and culturally refined\" vibe. It evokes a sense of established wealth and traditional elegance through its colonial mansions and manicured grounds. The focus on private clubs and historical landmarks suggests a refined, exclusive lifestyle. Option B is too chaotic, and Option C leans more toward vibrant community than rarefied prestige.",
