      "content": "I see. So you're essentially saying that \"refined\" is synonymous with that \"European-style\" aesthetic you mentioned. \n\nIf I were to rewrite Option C to include more high-end amenities—like boutique luxury shops or upscale dining—would it then lose its \"soulful/communal\" label and become more prestigious? Or is there still a fundamental difference in how a client would view a neighborhood with deep ethnic roots versus a more traditionally Western one?",
